          <div id="homeid" class="col-sm-8">
        <h1>Complex Additive Materials Group</h1>

	<p>We are the <strong>Mind Lab</strong>, based in the <a href="https://www.binghamton.edu/mechanical-engineering/">Department of Mechanical Engineering</a> at <a href="https://www.binghamton.edu">Binghamton University</a>. Our research integrates <strong>artificial intelligence</strong>, <strong>materials science</strong>, and <strong>computational chemistry</strong> to accelerate discovery and design of advanced materials for <strong>energy</strong>, <strong>environmental sustainability</strong>, and <strong>healthcare applications</strong>.</p>

